---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Бидний тухай">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#003375]/10 via-[#f7941e]/10 to-white"></div>
        <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
                        Титэм Плаза — Ховдын итгэлтэй худалдааны төв
                    </h1>
                    <p class="mt-5 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        Бид чанартай бүтээгдэхүүн, тав тухтай үйлчилгээ, найдвартай түншлэлээрээ хэрэглэгч бүрийн хэрэгцээг хангахыг зорьдог.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
                        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#f7941e] text-white hover:bg-[#e28316] shadow">
                            Холбоо барих
                        </a>
                        <a href="/products" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white hover:bg-gray-800 shadow">
                            Бүтээгдэхүүн харах
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
                    <img src="../address.jpg" alt="Титэм Плаза байршил" class="w-full max-w-lg rounded-2xl shadow-2xl object-cover h-72 md:h-96 ring-1 ring-black/5" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
            <div class="bg-white/70 rounded-xl shadow p-6 md:p-8 order-2 md:order-1">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Бидний зорилго</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    Титэм Плаза нь Ховд аймгийн хэрэглэгчдэд чанартай үйлчилгээ, найдвартай бүтээгдэхүүн хүргэх зорилготой худалдааны төв юм. Манай хамт олон таны хэрэгцээнд нийцсэн шийдлийг санал болгож, үргэлж хөгжиж дэвшиж байх болно.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/70 rounded-xl shadow p-6 md:p-8 order-1 md:order-2">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Холбоо барих</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-800">
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#f7941e] mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
                        <span class="font-semibold">Утас:</span>
                        <a href="tel:+97699116396" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline ml-2 break-all">+976 9911-6396</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#1877f2] mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.879V14.89h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.505 1.492-3.891 3.776-3.891 1.094 0 2.24.195 2.24.195v2.453h-1.26c-1.247 0-1.664.776-1.664 1.57v1.88h2.773l-.443 2.98h-2.33v6.189C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10z"/></svg>
                        <span class="font-semibold">Facebook:</span>
                        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61555220827287" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline ml-2 break-all">Ховд-Титэм плаза</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#f7941e] mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8m-18 4v7a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7m-18 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v7"/></svg>
                        <span class="font-semibold">Имэйл:</span>
                        <a href="mailto:info@titemplaza.mn" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline ml-2 break-all">info@titemplaza.mn</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#f7941e] mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.828 0l-4.243-4.243m10.606-10.607a4 4 0 11-5.656 0 4 4 0 015.656 0zm-5.656 0L12 10.001l-1.414-1.414m-5.657 5.657a8 8 0 1011.314 0l-5.657-5.657z" /></svg>
                        <span class="font-semibold">Хаяг:</span>
                        <span class="ml-2">Ховд аймаг, Жаргалант сум, Титэм Плаза</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Бидний үнэ цэнэ</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Чанар</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Бид зөвхөн шалгарсан, найдвартай нийлүүлэгчдээс бүтээгдэхүүнээ авдаг.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Үйлчилгээ</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Хэрэглэгч бүрт тохирсон тусламж үйлчилгээ үзүүлэхийг эрхэмлэдэг.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Шинэлэг байдал</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Үргэлж сайжруулж, шинэ санаачилгуудыг хэрэгжүүлдэг.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pb-20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Бидний байршил</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl w-full h-80 md:h-96">
            <iframe
                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2172.442642547064!2d91.6413503159991!3d48.00583090000001!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x5dcae3b6e2c1b6b7%3A0x7e6c6e7e7e7e7e7e!2z0KLQvtC70YzQvdCw0Y8g0J_QvtC70YzQvdCw0Y8LCBIeXBlIENhZmUsINCQ0LvQvtC00L7QvNC40Y8g0J_QvtC70YzQvdCw0Y8!5e0!3m2!1smn!2smn!4v1718001234567!5m2!1smn!2smn"
                width="100%"
                height="100%"
                style="border:0;"
                allowfullscreen=""
                loading="lazy"
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            ></iframe>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
